name: MISONR BCS Section 08 Health and Wellbeing
description: OAS0023 v1.0 Report to show BCS Section 8 answers for the selected establishment.

dataset.name: MIS Sentence
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.SURNAME, AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.INITIALS, AT_DIM_LOCATION.UNIT_4_SHORT_DESCRIPTION FROM BODIMIS.DIM_CELL AT_DIM_LOCATION, BODIMIS.DIM_ESTABLISHMENT AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP, BODIMIS.DIM_OFFENDER_BOOKING AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING WHERE (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK IN (SELECT CSL.OFFENDER_BOOKING_SK FROM BODIMIS.DIM_STAFF_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOAD SAC, BODIMIS.DIM_CASELOAD_SECURITY_LIST CSL WHERE SAC.CASELOAD_ID = CSL.CASELOAD_CODE AND SAC.USERNAME = (SELECT username FROM context_) AND CSL.ENDYEAR >= TO_CHAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, 'YYYY') - 6)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ESTABLISHMENT_SK = AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_SK) AND (AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_SK = AT_DIM_LOCATION.UNIT_4_SK (+)) AND ((AT_ESTABLISHMENT_TAP.ESTABLISHMENT_CODE_NK = (SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.MIS_CURRENT_RECORD_IND = 'Y'))), dataset_ AS (SELECT OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, SURNAME, INITIALS, UNIT_4_SHORT_DESCRIPTION, SURNAME || ', ' || INITIALS AS V_OFFENDER_SURNAME, CASE WHEN MENTAL_HEALTH_PROBLEMS = 1 THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS V_S8_IMMEDIATE_CARE_OR_HEALT38 FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: S8 Health & Well-being
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT ASSESSMENT.ASSESSMENT_ID, ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.BCS_PART1_COMP_DATE, ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.RECEPTION_DATE, BCS_PART_STATUS.DESCRIPTION, OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.HEALTH_CARE_SCREENING, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.REGISTERED_WITH_GP, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.SS_SUPPORT, DRUGS_ALCOHOL.DESCRIPTION AS DRUGS_ALCOHOL_PROBLEM, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.MENTAL_HEALTH_SERVICES, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.MENTAL_HEALTH_PROBLEMS, DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY.DESCRIPTION AS DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.S8_ISSUE_TO_BE_ADDRESSED FROM ASSESSMENT, ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID, BCS_PART_STATUS, OFFENDER, ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8, DRUGS_ALCOHOL, DRUGS_ALCOHOL DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY, REP_OFFENDER_HISTORY, PURPOSE_OF_BCSREASON WHERE (OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID = ASSESSMENT.OFFENDER_ID (+)) AND (OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID = REP_OFFENDER_HISTORY.OFFENDER_ID (+)) AND (ASSESSMENT.ASSESSMENT_ID = ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.ASSESSMENT_ID AND ASSESSMENT.ASSESSMENT_TYPE_ELM = 'TR_BCS') AND (PURPOSE_OF_BCSREASON.PURPOSE_OF_BCSREASON_CODE (+) = ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.BCS_PURPOSE) AND (ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.ASSESSMENT_ID = ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.ASSESSMENT_ID) AND (BCS_PART_STATUS.BCS_PART_STATUS_CODE (+) = ASSESSMENT_BCS_CASEID.BCS_PART1_STATUS) AND (ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.DRUGS_ALCOHOL_PROBLEM = DRUGS_ALCOHOL.DRUGS_ALCOHOL_CODE (+)) AND (ASSESSMENT_BCS_SECTION8.DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY = DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY.DRUGS_ALCOHOL_CODE (+)) AND (SUBSTR(OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, 1, 10) = TAGMIS_CASELOAD_SECURITY('VQL10O', OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY)) AND ((REP_OFFENDER_HISTORY.LATEST_OWNERSHIP_RANK = 1) AND BCS_PART_STATUS.DESCRIPTION = 'Complete' AND PURPOSE_OF_BCSREASON.DESCRIPTION IN ('Basic Custody Screening - Start') AND REP_OFFENDER_HISTORY.PHYSICAL_LOCATION IN ('Bedford (HMP)'))), dataset_ AS (SELECT ASSESSMENT_ID, BCS_PART1_COMP_DATE, RECEPTION_DATE, DESCRIPTION, OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, HEALTH_CARE_SCREENING, REGISTERED_WITH_GP, SS_SUPPORT, DRUGS_ALCOHOL_PROBLEM, MENTAL_HEALTH_SERVICES, MENTAL_HEALTH_PROBLEMS, DRUGS_ALCOHOL_AGENCY, S8_ISSUE_TO_BE_ADDRESSED, COUNTDISTINCT(MIS_SENTENCE.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY) OVER (PARTITION BY ASSESSMENT_ID = V_MAX_ASSESSMENT_ID) AS V_S8_NOMS_NUMBER, SURNAME || ', ' || INITIALS AS V_OFFENDER_SURNAME, CASE WHEN MENTAL_HEALTH_PROBLEMS = 1 THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END AS V_S8_IMMEDIATE_CARE_OR_HEALT38 FROM dataset_base_)

field.name: $ref:V_S8_NOMS_NUMBER
field.display: B8.5 Have you ever had any contact with a drug or alcohol agency?
field.legacySql: =Count([MIS Sentence].[NOMS Number];Distinct) Where ([Assessment ID] = [v_Max Assessment ID])

field.name: $ref:V_S8_NOMS_NUMBER
field.legacySql: =Count([MIS Sentence].[NOMS Number];Distinct) Where ([Assessment ID] = [v_Max Assessment ID])

filter.name: prefilter_
filter.query: prefilter_ AS (SELECT * FROM dataset_ WHERE V_MAX_ASSESSMENT_ID_FOR_FILTER IN (1))

field.name: $ref:V_OFFENDER_SURNAME
field.display: B8.1 Has the health care screening been completed on reception?

field.name: $ref:V_S8_HEALTH_CARE_SCREENING
field.display: B8.2 Are you registered with a GP?

field.name: $ref:V_S8_REGISTERED_WITH_GP
field.display:
B8.3 Have you ever received
support from Social Services or
Social Care Services?

field.name: $ref:V_S8_SOCIAL_SERVICES_SUPPORT
field.display: B8.4 Have drugs and /or alcohol ever been a problem for you?

field.name: $ref:V_S8_MENTAL_HEALTH_SERVICES
field.display: B8.7 Do you have any care or health problems for which you require immediate attention or medication, or which might impact on your day-to-day ability to engage with the prison regime?

field.name: $ref:V_S8_IMMEDIATE_CARE_OR_HEALT38
field.display:
B8.9 Is Health & Well-being an issue which needs addressing? 
[For the screener to consider]

field.name: $ref:V_S8_ISSUE_TO_BE_ADDRESSED
field.legacySql: =If([S8 Issue To Be Addressed]=0;"No";(If([S8 Issue To Be Addressed]=1;"Yes";"Don't Know")))
